  Source:
    Title: Harijan
    Editor: Mohandas Gandhi
    Locus:
      Date: 24 November 1933
---
It is not given to man to know the whole Truth. His duty lies in living up
to the Truth as he sees it and in doing so to resort to the purest means,
i.e., to non-violence.
